    "An explicit instruction was added to ensure the shortest rotational path (clockwise or counterclockwise) was always chosen when adjusting the heading.",
    "1 You a r e an a g e n t i n a 2D s i m u l a t i o n.",
    "By explicitly instructing the model to select the shortest path to the target heading, flocking behavior improved significantly.",
    "The LLM-driven agents formed larger, more stable flocking clusters, achieving performance comparable to the original, rule-based NetLogo model.",
    "Including the shortest-path directive ensured that LLM-based agents correctly aligned their heading adjustments with both LLM-based and rule-based agents."
